  "texts": [
    "Due to the inherent instability in the results generated by the LLM, a consistent structure is employed to ensure the accuracy of the generated Cypher queries.",
    "The model populates the extracted entities within the predefined structure to produce the Cypher queries.",
    "The generated Cypher queries are then sent to the knowledge graph for execution, returning the entity nodes pertinent to the user's query, along with the relationships between these entities.",
    "Based on the results returned from the knowledge graph, the system formulates a response to be presented to the user.",
    "This procedure ensures the precision and pertinence of the response, as illustrated in Figure 6."
  ],
